      "role": "user",
      "content": "But if you let every group opt out whenever they feel like it, doesn't that just create a two-tier system of laws? Like, how can a democracy function if certain organizations are basically above the rules that everyone else has to follow? Isn't the principle of equality under the law more vital for stability?",
